Case study Problem Statement	

Software System lets Admin to upload Stock Price of a Company(which is listed in a Stock Exchange) at different points of time.

System supports View history of mentors (including past ratings), addition of new technical courses, mentor management and training progress tracking.


Actors
Administrator – Add/Edit/Delete/View users, stocks and exchanges.
User – Generate various charts for stock market performance
   

Services

Admin User Service add/Delete, View/Modify user details 	
Admin Stock Service add/Delete, View/Modify stock.	
Admin Exchange Service  add/Delete, View/Modify stock to exchanges
Admin Excel bulk upload/download service for adding stocks
User Graph service to generate charts for performance
TECHNOLOGY USED
JAVA 8​
Postgres
Spring Boot
Angular

